Description of files/folders:

qualification_test:
	contains guidelines for annotators.
	contains qualification test and its related files.
	contains list of annotators along with their demographic details.
	Some of the annotators' (around 10 annotators) demographic details are absent due to a technical problem beyond our control.
	For ethical reasons, all the workerID's are anonymized.

mturk_hits:
	contains all the mturk hits as displayed to the annotators.
	_1 and _2 file extensions correspond to the hits related to first and second constituents of a compound respectively.

annotations:
	contains all the annotations
	columns of each file correspond to "word	workerID	hitID	status	score	senseID	remarks" (all separated by tab).
	hitID is for our internal purpose and you will not need it.
	_1 and _2 file extensions correspond to the annotations of first and second constituents of a compound respectively.
	
MeanAndDeviations.clean.txt:
	This file contains mean and std deviation scores computed from all the accepted hits.


Please cite our paper if you use this dataset:

